      "created_at": "2022-02-16T14:08:42.742Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I would suggest adding a sound function that signals the given cadence (for both pedals). The frequency could be automatically adjusted if there is a given cadence in the training. And in a situation where it is not defined in the training - it is turned on by pressing a button on the screen if the correct cadence is reached.</p>",
