    {
      "id": 5820,
      "name": "Roy Hellinga",
      "username": "e-sarge",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/e/bc79bd/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2022-02-21T20:07:39.151Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Maybe in resistance mode it would work, but in ERG mode it\u2019s too difficult (I\u2019ve tried to match the beat of the music). Between the flywheel weight (which slows down your reaction time) and the resistance constantly changing, it\u2019s very difficult to be that exact with the RPM.</p>\n<p>For reference, in spin class with just a flywheel and fixed resistance, I was able to do it pretty well.</p>",
