      "cooked": "<p>What about this?  or you can buy an cheap metronome <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"> Just talking ideas here.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/6/6b63e446c0f5a651ae36217cbd73eda8949aa7e6.png\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/6b63e446c0f5a651ae36217cbd73eda8949aa7e6\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/6b63e446c0f5a651ae36217cbd73eda8949aa7e6_2_690x345.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"fk16AIYwEhrf7Rhk7G0r2o3MzMa\" width=\"690\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/6b63e446c0f5a651ae36217cbd73eda8949aa7e6_2_690x345.png, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/6b63e446c0f5a651ae36217cbd73eda8949aa7e6_2_1035x517.png 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/6b63e446c0f5a651ae36217cbd73eda8949aa7e6_2_1380x690.png 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/6b63e446c0f5a651ae36217cbd73eda8949aa7e6_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1774\u00d7888 43.2 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
