      "id": 6343,
      "name": "Mariusz",
      "username": "mowczar",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/47e85d/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2022-04-05T11:02:30.104Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I use an app like this during my workouts <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.smp.naturalmetronome&amp;hl=pl\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.smp.naturalmetronome&amp;hl=pl</a><br>\nbut unfortunately when I change the cadence in a training task, the rhythm set in this application remains.<br>\nImplementing such a function in TrainerDay app in my opinion would increase its training functionality. In any case, I miss it. Because I wouldn\u2019t have to keep track on my smartphone screen of my current cadence and whether it is the same as in the training task, because I would hear that either I don\u2019t keep the rhythm or it has changed.</p>",
